# Project Configuration

> This file defines project-specific variables used in other rules via `${VARIABLE}` syntax.

## Project Identity

| Variable | Value |
|----------|-------|
| PROJECT_NAME | [YourProject] |
| PROJECT_TYPE | [e.g., Django backend + React frontend] |
| PROJECT_TECH_STACK | [e.g., Django, DRF, PostgreSQL, React, TypeScript] |
| CODE_COMMENT_LANGUAGE | [English/other] |

