## Project Structure

| Variable | Value |
|----------|-------|
| PROJECT_STRUCTURE_TYPE | [workspace/single] |
| PROJECT_PARTS | [backend:${BACKEND_PATH}, frontend:${FRONTEND_PATH}] |

<!-- PROJECT_STRUCTURE_TYPE: workspace (multiple apps) | single (one app) -->
<!-- PROJECT_PARTS: comma-separated list of "name:path" pairs, e.g., "backend:backend, frontend:client-web, mobile:mobile-app" -->

